profile.bio:
Dashboard Team Lead @ Cisco Meraki.

In various past lives: research scientist @ Intel Research Berkeley, postdoc @ MIT, graduate student @ UC Berkeley, and bicycle racer for Metromint Cycling and Essex County Velo. Founder of the GoldenCheetah project.
